quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,“۞ Kodi akufunsana zachiyani
  78,2,“Za nkhani yayikulu ija
  78,3,“Imene iwo akusiyana (maganizo)
  78,4,“Aleke (zimenezo) adzadziwa posachedwapa
  78,5,"“Ayi, ndithu aleke (zimenezo); posachedwapa adzadziwa zoona zake (pamene chilango chidzawatsikira)"
  78,6,“Kodi sitidachite nthaka kukhala ngati choyala
  78,7,“Ndi mapiri ngati zichiri (zolimbitsa nthaka)
  78,8,“Ndipo takulengani mitundu iwiri (amuna ndi akazi)
  78,9,“Ndipo tidachita tulo tanu kukhala mpumulo (ku mavuto a ntchito)
  78,10,“Ndipo taupanga usiku kukhala ngati chovala (pokuvindikirani ndi mdima wake)
  78,11,“Ndipo tapanga masana kukhala nthawi yopezera zofunika pa moyo
  78,12,“Ndipo tamanga pamwamba panu thambo zisanu ndi ziwiri zolimba
  78,13,“Ndipo tidapanga nyali yowala ndi yotentha kwambiri (dzuwa)
  78,14,"“Ndipo tawatsitsa madzi otsika mwamphamvu kuchokera ku mitambo, ya mvula"
  78,15,"“Kuti titulutse ndi madziwo mbewu ndi m’mera, (chomwe ndi chakudya cha anthu ndi nyama)"
  78,16,“Ndi minda yothothana nthambi za mitengo
  78,17,“Ndithu tsiku la chiweruziro ndinthawi imene idakhazikitsidwa kale
  78,18,“Tsiku limene lipenga (lakuuka) lidzaimbidwa ndipo inu mudzabwera (kubwalo losonkhanirana) muli magulumagulu
  78,19,"“Ndipo thambo lidzatsegulidwa (mbali zonse): choncho lidzakhala makomomakomo"
  78,20,"“Ndipo mapiri adzachotsedwa m’malo mwake, adzakhala ngati zideruderu"
  78,21,“Ndithu moto wa Jahannam ukuwadikilira (oipa)
  78,22,“Mbuto ya opyola malire
  78,23,“Adzakhala m’menemo muyaya
  78,24,"“Sadzalawa m’menemo kuzizira (kowachotsera kutentha), kapena chakumwa (chowachotsera ludzu lawo)"
  78,25,“Kupatula madzi otentha kwambiri ndi mafinya (otuluka mmatupi a anthu a ku Moto)
  78,26,“Kukhala malipiro olingana ndi ntchito zawo
  78,27,“Ndithu iwo sadali kuyembekezera chiwerengero (cha Allah)
  78,28,“Adatsutsa zizindikiro Zathu (zosonyeza kuuka kwa akufa) ndi mtsutso waukulu
  78,29,“Ndipo chinthu chilichonse tachisunga mochilemba
  78,30,"“Basi, lawani (lero chilango Changa); sitikuonjezerani chinthu china koma chilango pamwamba pa chilango"
  78,31,“Ndithu anthu oopa Allah adzakhala ndi malo wopambana
  78,32,“Minda ndi zipatso za mphesa
  78,33,“Ndi mabuthu (anamwali) ofanana misinkhu
  78,34,“Ndi zipanda zodzaza ndi zakumwa
  78,35,“Sakamva m’menemo mawu opanda pake kapena bodza
  78,36,“Amenewa ndi malipiro ochokera kwa Mbuye wako zopereka zokwanira
  78,37,“Mbuye wa kumwamba ndi pansi ndi zimene zili pakati pake; Wachifundo chambiri. Palibe amene adzakhala ndi mphamvu yolankhulana naye (pa tsiku limenero)
  78,38,“Tsiku limene adzaima Jibril ndi angelo pa mzere (ali odzichepetsa); sadzayankhula aliyense mwa iwo kupatula yekhayo amene adzaloledwa ndi (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri (kuyankhula) ndipo adzanena zolondola
  78,39,"“Limenelo ndi tsiku loona, (lopanda chikaiko); choncho amene akufuna adzipezere malo (njira yonkera) kwa Mbuye wake. (Pomugonjera Iye pa moyo uno wadziko lapansi)"
  78,40,"“Ndithu tikukuchenjezani zachilango chomwe chili pafupi kudza; tsiku limene munthu adzayang’ana zimene adatsogoza manja ake, ndipo wosakhulupirira adzanena: Kalanga ine! Ndikadakhala dothi, (kuti ndisalangidwe chilango chikundiyembekezachi)"